Author: MyNamelessFace
Text: When I'm stressed or sad or frustrated, in the first seconds I feel like: "I don't want to eat ever again... " and minutes later I binged on 1000kcal or more. I hate it.

Author: Panic-atthepanic
Text: You always deserve to live. I'm sorry you don't feel comfortable in your body right now, it's an awful feeling.  But you definitely deserve to live, and no matter your size you're beautiful.  It's hard living with something like this.
